    <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Lacunose, illustrated copy of the Quintet, containing all of Iskandarnāmah and Laylī va Majnūn. Makhzan al-asrār is missing the beginning and the end; Haft paykar ends abruptly, and Khusraw va Shīrīn is missing all but the final page. This copy contains 19 full-page illustrations, numerous gold and polychrome decorative text division markers and foliate in-fill around angled lines and at the end of each work.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
