    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="505" ind1="0" ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">1. f. 1v-130v: Sharaf-nāmah-ʼi Iskandarī -- 2. f. 131r: Final page of Khusraw va Shīrīn -- 3. f. 131v-187v: Laylī va Majnūn -- 4. f. 187v-Haft paykar [incomplete] -- 5. f. 256r-282v: Makhzan al-asrār [incomplete]</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="530" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
